// {{pascal .pipeline_name}} runs a single guarded job. The
// contentkey.Unchanged predicate compares the watched paths against the
// base ref and skips the job when nothing under them moved, so an
// unrelated change never pays for this work. A base ref that does not
// resolve fails safe: the predicate reports changed and the job runs.
type {{pascal .pipeline_name}} struct{ sparkwing.Base }

